            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>Imp</abbr><ex>erator</ex></expan> Caesar Divi <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>August</abbr><ex>us</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>pontif</abbr><ex>ex</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>maxim</abbr><ex>us</ex></expan> flumen Sebaston <lb n="3"/>ab schedia induxit a milliario <lb n="4"/>XXV quod per se toto oppido flueret <lb n="5"/>praefecto Aegypti <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aio</ex></expan> Iulio Aquila anno <lb n="6"/>XXXX Caesaris </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Αὐτοκράτωρ Καῖσαρ θεοῦ υἱὸς Σεβαστὸς <lb n="2"/>ἀρχιερεὺς ποταμὸν Σεβαστὸν ἀπὸ <lb n="3"/>Σχεδίας ἤγαγεν ἐπὶ σταδ<supplied reason="lost">ίου</supplied>ς διακοσίους <lb n="4"/>ῥέοντα δι’ ὅλης τῆς πόλεως ἐπὶ ἐπάρχου <lb n="5"/>τῆς Αἰγύπτου Γαΐου Ἰουλίου Ἀκύλα <lb n="6"/>(ἔτους) μʹ Καίσαρος
            </ab></div></div>
